name: This Lead Generation AI Agent Scrapes Unlimited Leads For FREE

parameters.content:
## Step 5 — Write & Continue

Append or update one row per website in Google Sheets with: Email(s) (aggregated), Website, Keyword, Location, Phone.
Matching column is Website; Value Input Mode is RAW to avoid formula parsing.
Short pause, then continue the loop.

## Step 4 — Combine & Extract Emails

Merge all fetched HTML, extract valid emails, and detect phone.
Role inboxes like info@/contact@ are allowed; assets, trackers, placeholders, and image-size false positives are filtered out.
If no email is found, the email cell carries a clear note; phone is always filled (or “No phone listed”).

## Step 3 — Fetch Pages (per website)

For each site, fetch the homepage, pause briefly, then try /contact and /contact-us to maximize email hit-rate while staying free.
These fetch nodes are set to Continue On Fail and Always Output Data so the run never breaks on a missing page.

## Step 2 — Parse & Prep Websites

Fetch Google Maps results HTML, extract candidate websites, drop junk (google/gstatic/schema), de-dupe, then limit to your requested count for a fast demo.
Outputs a clean list of websites into the loop.

## Step 1 — Inputs (Form)

Collect run variables from the form: Keyword, Location, Max Leads.
Maps them to consistent fields in Edit Fields.
Keeps the template free: no API keys required, only Google Sheets.

parameters.formTitle: Lead Generation AI Agent – Free Google Maps Scraper
parameters.formDescription:
Enter your lead search details below and click Submit to start scraping.
The AI Agent will find businesses from Google Maps, visit their websites, and collect publicly available emails automatically.
All results are saved in your connected Google Sheet — no paid APIs or sign-ups needed.
